name picinpar
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc Insert pictures into paragraphs
longdesc A legacy package for creating 'windows' in paragraphs, for
longdesc inserting graphics, etc. (including "dropped capitals"). Users
longdesc should note that Pieter van Oostrum (in a published review of
longdesc packages of this sort) does not recommend this package; Picins
longdesc is recommended instead.
